</div></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-richtitle"><p class="field-content"><a href="https://worldliteraturetoday.org/blog/book-reviews/reassessing-exile-and-diaspora-review-exile-and-jews-and-letters-home-alan">Reassessing Exile and Diaspora: A Review of <em>Exile and the Jews</em>…</a>
</p></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-author"><span class="views-label views-label-field-author field-name-field-blogauthor">By</span><span class="field-content field-name-field-blogauthor"><a href="/author/alan-levenson" hreflang="en">Alan Levenson</a>
</span></div>
